        "description": "A synthesis of multiple prior studies on CFD-based hemolysis modelling, integrating the Giersiepen–Wurzinger power-law damage accumulation model with updated empirical coefficients from three independent experimental campaigns (Zhang et al. 2011, Taskin et al. 2012, Arvand et al. 2005). This node aggregates parameter estimates for the hemolysis exponent α and stress coefficient C, providing the calibrated input basis for the validation comparison. The synthesis was conducted by the modelling team as part of the pre-study literature review and is well-documented in the internal technical report TR-CPB-2023-04."
