      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match simulated boundary conditions within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments conducted at 37°C with bovine blood analog (glycerol-saline) at matched viscosity. Flow rates controlled to ±2% of target values. Rotational speed verified via optical tachometer. Boundary condition correspondence documented in TR-CPB-2023-04."
    },
    {
